name: Metamorph - Stygian Acheronsis
description:
Stygian Acheronsis is a Troglobites of the Metamorph species that lives in a sparkling cave, the cave is called the Shimmermist Cavern. This creature has an egg-like shape that he uses to capture light from sparkling crystal rocks as food. Its sparkling scales are a radiant glow as a result of its digestion as a light-consuming creature.

Stygian Acheronsis is the first subspecies of the Metacreatura species to appear in the Metacreatura series.
